metadata.name: A Day in May
metadata.description:
A Day in May is a generative NFT and plotter painting. 10 colors are selected semi-randomly from a pre-determined set of 70 possibilities. 45,600 generative brushstrokes fill the canvas. 

The NFT is 8000 x 10000

**Physical Plotter Painting**
Size Unframed: 24” x 30” 
Number of Colors: 10 
Medium: Acrylic paint on canvas
